message.content: cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE. The paper is about a dataset for machine reading comprehension, which falls under the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). Information retrieval (cs.IR) is also relevant as the dataset is based on Wikipedia articles. Neural networks (cs.NE) may also be relevant as they are commonly used in MRC tasks.
